**Start from** the middle of Shap the day is spent walking South broadly in parallel with the M6.

Transport. The 106 bus runs along the A6 between Penrith  and Shap. There are busses between Tebay and Penrith and Tebay and Kendal, but only on a Tuesday, Wednesady or Friday. Time this leg well, if you're relying on public transport.

